{"id": 117168, "slug": "tetris-midi", "name": "TETRIS MIDI", "name_original": "TETRIS MIDI", "description": "--------------------------------------------\r\n-- TETRIS MIDI Keyboard Edition ------------\r\n\r\nA game crafted at #ZooMachines 2016 by\r\n Leon Denise - shader programming - (@leondenise) \r\n Ivan Notaros - shader programming - (@Nothke)\r\n Boris Warembourg - music - (#GrizzlyCogs)\r\n Damien Chouchen - gameplay programming - (@metalchouchen)\r\n \r\nSource can be found on github\r\n\r\n--------------------------------------------\r\nTETRIS MIDI is a 1 vs 1 tetris game, when \r\nplayers cumulate rows the game switch to the \r\n2nd game mode.\r\nThe game is used to be played with a midi \r\ncontroller but works fine with a classic \r\ndesktop keyboard since #Screenshake17\r\n--------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n1st game mode : COLOR IS ROTATION\r\n--------------------------------------------\r\n|shape | player 1      | player 2         |\r\n|------|---------------|------------------|\r\n|      |midi |keyboard |midi |keyboard    |\r\n|------|---------------|------------------|\r\n|Rotation                                 | \r\n|-----------------------------------------|\r\n|I     |0x32 |A        |0x47 |P           |\r\n|L     |0x35 |Z        |0x43 |O           |\r\n|J     |0x37 |Z        |0x41 |O           |\r\n|S     |0x3B |R        |0x3E |U           |\r\n|Z     |0x39 |R        |0x40 |U           |\r\n|O     |0x34 |E        |0x45 |I           |\r\n|T     |0x30 |T        |0x48 |Y           |\r\n--------------------------------------------\r\n|Move                                     |\r\n--------------------------------------------\r\n|fall  |0x18 |D        |0x1F |K           |\r\n|left  |0x39 |Q        |0x40 |L           |\r\n|right |0x39 |S        |0x40 |M           |\r\n--------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n--------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n2nd game mode : SLIDER OUT OF SYNC\r\n--------------------------------------------\r\n|         | player 1      | player 2      |\r\n|---------|---------------|---------------|\r\n|         |midi |keyboard |midi |keyboard |\r\n|---------|---------------|---------------|\r\n|slider 1 |0x00 |A and Q  |0x04 |U and J  |\r\n|slider 2 |0x01 |Z and S  |0x05 |I and K  |\r\n|slider 3 |0x02 |E and D  |0x06 |O and L  |\r\n|slider 4 |0x03 |R and F  |0x07 |P and M  |\r\n--------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n--------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n--------------------------------------------\r\n|             |midi |keyboard             |\r\n|-------------|---------------------------|\r\n|Restart Game |0x6A |N+SPACE              |\r\n|Quit Game    |     |ESCAPE               |\r\n--------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nHave a nice play &amp; enjoy the shaders,\r\nDamien;\r\n--------------------------------------------", "metacritic": null, "released": "2017-02-14", "tba": false, "updated": "2019-01-09T12:41:06", "background_image": "https://media.rawg.io/media/screenshots/e97/e9710108d6cee3593d685e8f8d7e6d92.jpg", "website": "", "rating": 0.0, "rating_top": 0, "added_by_status": null, "playtime": 0, "achievements_count": 0, "ratings_count": 0, "suggestions_count": 128, "game_series_count": 0, "reviews_count": 0, "platforms": ["PC"], "developers": ["MetalChouchen"], "genres": ["Puzzle"], "publishers": [], "esrb_rating": null}